<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Telegram中文版 - 两分钟规避SMSfee</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: white;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .problem-section {
            border-left: 5px solid #ff6b6b;
        }

        .problem-section h2 {
            color: #ff6b6b;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .problem-box {
            background: #fff5f5;
            border: 2px solid #ff6b6b;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #c92a2a;
        }

        .solution-section h2 {
            color: #51cf66;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .step {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .step:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .step-content h3 {
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .step-content p {
            color: #868e96;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #a8edea 0%, #fed6e3 100%);
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #495057;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .warning {
            background: #fff9db;
            border-left: 4px solid #fcc419;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        .warning strong {
            color: #f08c00;
        }

        .features-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .features-section h2 {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: white;
        }

        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
        }

        .feature-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .feature-item h3 {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature-item p {
            font-size: 0.95em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            background: #51cf66;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(81, 207, 102, 0.4);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #40c057;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(81, 207, 102, 0.6);
        }

        .reward-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: #ffe066;
            color: #5c4800;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }
            .step {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            .feature-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .pulse {
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🚀 Telegram中文版</h1>
            <p>两分钟助您规避SMSfee问题，重返纸飞机！</p>
        </header>

        <!-- 抛问题 -->
        <div class="card problem-section">
            <h2>
                <span>⚠️</span>
                遇到这些问题？
            </h2>
            <div class="problem-box">
                账号退登、换号或更新后，极易触发 <strong>SMSfee 验证</strong>，导致重新登录失败。
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #666;">
                很多人在退登、换号或更新 Telegram 后，才遇到 SMSfee 问题，结果直接登不上号。
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 解决问题步骤 -->
        <div class="card solution-section">
            <h2>
                <span>✅</span>
                简单几步，轻松解决
            </h2>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>打开应用</h3>
                    <p>打开提前下好的 <span class="highlight">Telegram中文版</span>，点击<span class="highlight">"开始聊天"</span>，再点击右上角<span class="highlight">对勾</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>选择账号</h3>
                    <p>点击<span class="highlight">购买成品直登号</span>，可以看到很多国家的账号。以购买英国号码为例，点击付款即可</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 0.9em;">💳 支持支付宝、银行卡、信用卡、USDT、TRX等多种支付方式</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="warning">
                <strong>⚡ 重要提示：</strong>得到手机号后复制下来，<strong>一定要点击＋号后面的区域粘贴</strong>，点击"是"进行下一步
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>输入验证码</h3>
                    <p>点击<span class="highlight">获取验证码</span>，复制下来，粘贴上去</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>输入二次密码</h3>
                    <p>点击<span class="highlight">获取二次密码</span>，复制下来，粘贴上去</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step" style="background: #d3f9d8; border: 2px solid #51cf66;">
                <div class="step-number" style="background: #51cf66;">✓</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3 style="color: #2b8a3e;">登录成功！</h3>
                    <p>进来就是<span class="highlight">中文版</span>，无需下载翻译包！</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 25px; padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px;">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: #495057;">📱 功能一览</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">依次查看下方功能：<span class="highlight">联系人</span>、<span class="highlight">设置</span>、<span class="highlight">个人资料</span>、最后是<span class="highlight">我的</span></p>
                <div class="reward-badge">
                    🎁 邀请好友得奖励
                </div>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
                    满100即可提现，奖励永久有效，好友每次订阅您都有奖励！
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 再次强调重点 -->
        <div class="card features-section">
            <h2>
                <span>⭐</span>
                核心优势
            </h2>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🔌</div>
                    <h3>官方MTProto协议</h3>
                    <p>内置官方MTProto，官方原生协议，高速通道直连</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
                    <h3>无需魔法梯子</h3>
                    <p>有了它就不需要再打开任何魔法梯子，即开即用</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
                    <h3>原生中文版</h3>
                    <p>无需翻译包，打开就是中文版，使用无障碍</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
                    <h3>规避SMSfee</h3>
                    <p>有效解决退登、换号、更新后的验证问题</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a href="#" class="cta-button pulse">
                立即下载 Telegram中文版
            </a>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>Telegram中文版 · 让通信更简单</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
